## Project Structure

This project follows [The Five Tenets](legibility/architecture.md):

| Folder | Tenet | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `src/` | — | Reusable library/tooling code |
| `scripts/` | — | Pipeline steps (numerically ordered) |
| `reproducibility/` | Reproducibility | Docker, environments, infrastructure |
| `correctness/` | Correctness | Tests, contracts |
| `observability/` | Observability | Logging, monitoring, runbooks |
| `security/` | Security | Secrets, permissions, audit |
| `legibility/` | Legibility | Style guides, conventions, ADRs |

